																		Author Posts are for squares.
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1372582&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610183481" alt="Jacob Conwell" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1372582)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jacob-conwell" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1372582); return false;" >Jacob Conwell</a></span> <span class="odate time_1462516332 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">06 May 2016 06:32</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2504339">
									

<p>Alright! Now that Anderson Robotics is a big time GoI, it needs an official GoI hub. That was the goal I aimed to accomplish here.</p>
<p>Now, there are a few things that this hub is:</p>
<ul>
<li>A means of diving into the Anderson Robotics material for those unfamiliar with it.</li>
<li>A spring board for those interested in writing their own Anderson Robotics skip or tale.</li>
<li>A chronological listing of the already existing tales in the continuing series.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-373590-1" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-373590-1')">1</a></sup></li>
</ul>
<p>There are also a few things this hub is not:</p>
<ul>
<li>A canon.</li>
<li>A means of me to tell new writers what they can and cannot do with these characters.<sup class="footnoteref"><a id="footnoteref-373590-2" href="javascript:;" class="footnoteref" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnote-373590-2')">2</a></sup></li>
</ul>
<p>That being said, some serious thanks are in order.</p>
<p>Thank you <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1841781&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="A Random Day" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1841781)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/a-random-day" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1841781); return false;">A Random Day</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1814684&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="GreenWolf" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1814684)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/greenwolf" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1814684); return false;">GreenWolf</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735681&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="TwistedGears" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735681)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twis