<p>Special Thank You to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2005044&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="Decibelles" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2005044)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/decibelles" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2005044); return false;">Decibelles</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1735681&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="TwistedGears" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1735681)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/twistedgears" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1735681); return false;">TwistedGears</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1888434&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="djkaktus" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1888434)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/djkaktus" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1888434); return false;">djkaktus</a></span>, <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2203795&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="Kalinin" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2203795)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kalinin" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2203795); return false;">Kalinin</a></span>, and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1414765&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="Doctor Cimmerian" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1414765)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/doctor-cimmerian" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1414765); return false;">Doctor Cimmerian</a></span> for your contributions to the success of this GoI. You each added your own flavor to the concept, and the end products have been so much fun to read.</p>
<p>Finally, an extra special bonus thank you to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1621343&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1462516332" alt="SunnyClockwork" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1621343)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sunnyclockwork" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1621343); return false;">SunnyClockwork</a></span> for creating the slick new Anderson Robotics logo. You are the real MVP.</p>
<p>Enjoy the hub.</p>
<p>Conwell</p>
