														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2504606">
									

<p>Well, the business angle is also covered partially by The Factory and Doctor Wondertainment, in addition to AR, MC&amp;D, and PL.</p>
<p>Just as we have five religiously based GoIs: MC, HI, CotBG, Sarkcism, and Fifth Church.</p>
<p>And just as we have three local government GoIs: UIU, GRU-P, and ORIA.</p>
<p>My point with all this is that the GoI list has a ton of overlap in terms of the basic themes of what each group does. In my opinion, thats okay. In the vast anomalous world of the SCP universe the GoIs bleed into each other to create a rich fabric of characters, ideas, and organizations, rather than multiple boxes that are kept separate from each other.</p>

							</div>

								
					
