			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2510827">
									

<p>If the tale is set in a canon though (as the author comment on that page indicates), and it's included in the timeline, wouldn't that indicate that the canon and the GoI are tied together? What if someone wants to write the GoI outside of that canon? Or am I reading too much into that?</p>

